title: Impossible to stifle laughter on set — Dana Loesch tells about childhood altercation with chimp – TheBlaze
text:
Tweet 
Dana Loesch tells us her personal story about why she can’t stand monkeys. She explains how she got into a slap fight with a chimpanzee as a little kid because she believed it would be just like a human, but she soon found out that wasn’t the case. Dana will now have nothing to do with them.
